cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is primarily focused on robotics and learning control policies using a physics simulator. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses deep reinforcement learning techniques, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with image-based learning, which falls under the categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with sequential decision making, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
